<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Submission Failed - School Management System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="failure-page">
            <div class="failure-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i>
            </div>
            <h1>Submission Failed</h1>
            <div class="failure-message">
                <p>We're sorry, but your admission form could not be submitted at this time.</p>
                <div class="error-details">
                    <h2>Possible Reasons</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> Internet connection issues</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> Server maintenance</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> Form validation errors</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="support-info">
                        <h3>Need Help?</h3>
                        <p>If you continue to experience issues, please contact our support team:</p>
                        <div class="contact-details">
                            <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +1 234 567 890</p>
                            <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> support@school.com</p>
                            <p><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Support Hours: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="/admission" class="btn"><i class="fas fa-redo"></i> Try Again</a>
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Back to Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 